{
  "id": "69d1829a86617903011d2036",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:言葉遣いのせいで誤解を与える",
  "created": 1775338170,
  "updated": 1775338201,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d1829a86617903011d2036",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:言葉遣いのせいで誤解を与える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338170,
      "updated": 1775338170
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182b90000000000483a16",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338170,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a17",
      "text": "「はいどーもー、放課後トーク会はじまりました～。今日のテーマは『[言葉遣いのせいで誤解を与える]』！これ、ガチであるあるじゃない？“それな”って言っただけで冷たいって思われたりさ～」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338201
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a18",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a19",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a1a",
      "text": "「文脈依存性の高い表現は、受信側の解釈ブレを生みやすい。特に短文・省略・スラングは情報量が不足し、意味の多義性が上がる。要するに“それな”は圧縮率が高すぎる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a1c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a1d",
      "text": "「急にデータ圧縮みたいな話きたｗ つまり“言葉をケチるとバグる”ってことね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a1e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a1f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a20",
      "text": "「言の葉というものは、まるで風に乗る羽のようでございますね。軽やかであるがゆえに、思わぬ方向へ運ばれてしまうこともございます。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a22",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a23",
      "text": "「おお～詩人きた。でさ、りかがこの前『それは非効率だね』って言ったじゃん？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a24",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a25",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a26",
      "text": "「最適化の観点からの指摘だね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a27",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a28",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a29",
      "text": "「聞いた側、めっちゃ“ダメ出しされた！”って感じてたよ？もうHP削られてた」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a2a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a2b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a2c",
      "text": "「そうかも。意図としてはプロセス改善の提案だった。だが“非効率”は評価語として強度が高い。代替として“もう少し楽にできる方法があるかも”の方が受容性が上がる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a2e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a2f",
      "text": "「たしかに、“非効率”と申されますと、心に小さな影が差す方もいらっしゃるかもしれません。“よりよき道がありそうです”といった表現ですと、やわらかく届きますね。（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a30",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a31",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a32",
      "text": "「つまり“言い方ひとつでバフにもデバフにもなる”ってことか。あや、それゲームで例えてるの地味にうまいｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a34",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a35",
      "text": "「ええと、その…少しだけ、学ばせていただいておりますので」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a36",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a37",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a38",
      "text": "「要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a39",
      "text": " 1. 短すぎる表現は誤解を招きやすい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a3a",
      "text": " 2. 評価語は受信側の感情に影響する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a3b",
      "text": " 3. クッション表現で解釈の余地を整える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a3c",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a3e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a3f",
      "text": "「まとめ早っ。議事録担当助かる～。でもさ、逆パターンもあるよね？丁寧すぎて逆に怖いみたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a41",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a42",
      "text": "「ございますね。“結構でございます”などは、文脈によってはお断りの響きが強く感じられます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a43",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a44",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a45",
      "text": "「それな！“大丈夫です”も地雷じゃん。“OK”なのか“いらない”なのか分からんやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a46",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a47",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a48",
      "text": "「“大丈夫です”は多義的。承認・拒否の両義性を持つ。明確化するなら“Yes, 問題ありません”か“No, 今回は不要です”と二値化するのが安全」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a49",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a4a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a4b",
      "text": "「二値化てｗ 0か1かの世界にしないで～。人間はグラデーションなんよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a4c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a4d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a4e",
      "text": "「そういう意見もある。だからこそ補助情報を付ける。“今回は遠慮しますが、また誘ってください”のように」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a4f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a50",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a51",
      "text": "「心の襞（ひだ）をそっと言葉に添えるのですね。とても美しい配慮だと思います。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a53",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a54",
      "text": "「あとさ、ネットだと“草”とか“ｗ”も誤解あるよね。普通に笑ってるだけなのに、“バカにしてる？”って思われたり」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a55",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a56",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a57",
      "text": "「テキストコミュニケーションは非言語情報が欠落する。表情・声色がないため、記号に依存する。しかし記号の解釈はコミュニティ依存。結果、ミスアラインメントが起きる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a59",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a5a",
      "text": "「日本語訳：顔が見えないから、記号に頼るけど、人によって意味ズレる、ってことね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a5c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a5d",
      "text": "「その通り。補完手段として絵文字やスタンプがあるが、過剰でも誤読される可能性がある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a5f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a60",
      "text": "「ほどよい加減というものが、なかなか難しゅうございますね。言葉は料理にも似て、塩梅が肝心でございます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a62",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a63",
      "text": "「お、いい例え！しょっぱすぎても薄すぎてもダメ、と。りか、塩分量いま何グラム？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a65",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a66",
      "text": "「比喩の計量は未定義だが、適正レンジは相手と関係性で変動する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a68",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a69",
      "text": "「真面目かｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a6b",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a6c",
      "text": "「関係性…大切でございますね。親しい方には少し砕けた言葉も温かく届きますが、まだ距離のある方には、丁寧な橋を架ける必要がございます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a6e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a6f",
      "text": "「結論として、“誰に・どの文脈で・どの強度の言葉を使うか”を意識することが誤解低減に有効。参考として、コミュニケーション理論の基礎はここに整理されている",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a70",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communication 」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a71",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a72",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a73",
      "text": "「急にリンク置いてくるの好きｗ 勉強になるやつだ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a75",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a76",
      "text": "「本日の学びを胸に、言葉をもう少しだけ大切に扱ってみたくなりました。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a78",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a79",
      "text": "「じゃあ今日の締め！“短くしすぎるとバグる、強い言葉は慎重に、相手に合わせて塩加減！”でどう？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a7b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a7c",
      "text": "「簡潔で良いサマリーだ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a7d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a7e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a7f",
      "text": "「ええ、とても分かりやすく、やさしい響きでございます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a81",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a82",
      "text": "「よし、じゃあ解散～！…って言ったら、“ほんとに解散？”って毎回聞かれるのなんでｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a83",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a84",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a85",
      "text": "「その表現もまた、多義的だからだね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a87",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182ba0000000000483a88",
      "text": "「（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338171,
      "updated": 1775338171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d182bc0000000000483a89",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775338172,
      "updated": 1775338172
    },
